Package: hcpx
Title: HCP eXplorer - A Dataset Interface for Human Connectome Project Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", , "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0955-6606"))
Author: Bradley Buchsbaum [aut, cre] (0000-0003-0955-6606)
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Description: Turns HCP (Human Connectome Project) data into a local, queryable
    asset catalog with task/run awareness, plan-first downloads, reproducible
    manifests, and policy-aware metadata. Provides a table-first interface where
    everything is queryable with dplyr/dbplyr, and nothing downloads until
    explicitly requested.
